# Install Web Crawler Skill

This script will install the web-crawler-learner skill for you.

## Instructions

1. **Right-click** this file and select **"Run with PowerShell"**
2. The skill will be installed in:
   ```
   C:\Users\user\.openclaw\workspace\web-crawler-learner\
   ```
3. Once installed, you can use it like this:
   ```
   Learn about https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw
   ```

